### FullCalendar 
This is forked from [Adam Shaw's FullCalendar](https://github.com/arshaw/fullcalendar) and includes a `resourceDay` view.  This additional view shows resources horizontally and each resource's calendar vertically.

Please refer to the original project [documentation](http://arshaw.com/fullcalendar/docs/) for usage and available options.  For the `resourceDay` view usage, please refer to my [post](http://www.ikelin.com/jquery-fullcalendar-resource-day-view/).

The latest build can be downloaded [here](fullcalendar-1.5.4.zip).
